@The_Reaper_X wrote:

If you’ve been coding for 5 years you’d know not to ask whether or not to make a server. 5 years should give you enough experience to write a server from scratch with common sense to do it on your own with no input. Making a f2p server based on the input of mpsc forums makes it a little hard to believe you have that much experience.

Btw, you’re not supposed to ask a question like this in this section, let alone in any section really-- It should be common sense.
